{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Atomics.wait()","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/wait","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard-Objekte</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics\"><code>Atomics</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/add\"><code>Atomics.add()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/and\"><code>Atomics.and()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/compareExchange\"><code>Atomics.compareExchange()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/exchange\"><code>Atomics.exchange()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/isLockFree\"><code>Atomics.isLockFree()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/load\"><code>Atomics.load()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/notify\"><code>Atomics.notify()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/or\"><code>Atomics.or()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/store\"><code>Atomics.store()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/sub\"><code>Atomics.sub()</code></a></li><li><em><code>Atomics.wait()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/waitAsync\"><code>Atomics.waitAsync()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/xor\"><code>Atomics.xor()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong>Vererbung:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die statische <code><strong>Atomics</strong></code><strong><code>.wait()</code></strong> Methode verifiziert, dass eine gegebene Position in einem <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Int32Array\"><code>Int32Array</code></a> ein gegebene Wert ist und dann schläft und entweder aufgeweckt wird oder ein Timeout bekommt. Die Strings <code>\"ok\"</code>, <code>\"not-equal\"</code>, und <code>\"timed-out\"</code> sind alle möglichen Rückgabewerte</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Hinweis:</strong> Diese Operation funktioniert nur mit einem geteilten<strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Int32Array\"><code>Int32Array</code></a> und ist nicht im Main-Thread erlaubt.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">Atomics.wait(typedArray, index, value[, timeout])\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"typedarray\"><code>typedArray</code></dt>\n <dd>Ein geteiltes <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Int32Array\"><code>Int32Array</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"index\"><code>index</code></dt>\n <dd>Die Position im <code>typedArray</code>, an der gewartet wird.</dd>\n <dt id=\"value\"><code>value</code></dt>\n <dd>Der wert, mit dem getestet wird.</dd>\n <dt id=\"timeout\"><code>timeout</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>Wartezeit in Millisekunden. <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Infinity\"><code>Infinity</code></a>, wenn keine Zeit angegeben wird.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>String</code></a> welcher <code>\"ok\"</code>, <code>\"not-equal\"</code> oder <code>\"timed-out\"</code> ist.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceptions","title":"Exceptions","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Erzeugt einen <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a>, wenn <code>typedArray</code> kein&nbsp; <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Int32Array\"><code>Int32Array</code></a> ist.</li>\n <li>Erzeugt ein <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>RangeError</code></a>, wenn der <code>index</code> nicht in den Grenzen von <code>typedArray</code> ist.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beipsiele","title":"Beipsiele","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Gegeben ist ein <code>Int32Array</code>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> sab <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SharedArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1024</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> int32 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int32Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>sab<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Ein lesender Thread schläft und wartet auf Position 0, ander der Wert 0 erwartet wird. Solange diese gegeben ist, geht es nicht weiter. Immer wenn ein neuer schreibender Thread einen neuen Wert speichert, wacht der Thread. Im Anschluss ist der neue Wert an der Position 0 (123).</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>Atomics<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">wait</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>int32<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>int32<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 123</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Ein schreibender Thread speichert einen neuen Wert und wacht den wartenden Thread nach dem Schreiben auf.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>int32<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 0;</span>\nAtomics<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">store</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>int32<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">123</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nAtomics<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">wake</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>int32<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-atomics.wait\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Atomics.wait' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initiale Definition in ES2017.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Atomics.wait","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/wait/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics\"><code>Atomics</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/notify\"><code>Atomics.wake()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beipsiele","id":"beipsiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die statische Atomics.wait() Methode verifiziert, dass eine gegebene Position in einem Int32Array ein gegebene Wert ist und dann schläft und entweder aufgeweckt wird oder ein Timeout bekommt. Die Strings \"ok\", \"not-equal\", und \"timed-out\" sind alle möglichen Rückgabewerte","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Atomics.wait()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Atomics.wait()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Atomics.wait()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Atomics.wait()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/javascri